                                                                                                 1.2      Audience

                                                                                                 The primary audience for Part 2 is the set of federal government system owners and managers who
                                                                                                 are setting up or acquiring cryptographic key management capabilities. However, consistent with
                                                                                                 the Cybersecurity Enhancement Act of 2014 (PL 113-274), this Recommendation is also intended
                                                                                                 to provide cybersecurity guidelines to the private sector in addition to the government-focused
                                                                                                 guidance consistent with Office of Management and Budget (OMB) Circular A-130 (OMB 130 1).
                                                                                                 Since guidelines and best practices for the private sector are strictly voluntary, the requirement
